<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Offer Letter</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    table, th, td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
    }
    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Offer Letter</h1>
    <p>Dear {{full_name}},</p>
    <p>We are pleased to offer you the position of <strong>{{stack}}</strong> at our company.</p>
    <p>Your joining date is: <strong>{{date_of_joining}}</strong></p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 30px; color: #2c3e50;">CTC Details</h2>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Field</th>
        <th>Value</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Expected CTC</td>
        <td>{{expected_ctc}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Current CTC</td>
        <td>{{current_ctc}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Calculation<br/>(Expected CTC / 100) * 2 - Current CTC</td>
        <td>{{calculated_value}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>We look forward to having you on board!</p>
    <p>Regards,<br/>HR Team</p>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Company Name. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
